      <mj-section padding="0 25px" background-color="#FFFFFF">
        <mj-column width="100%">
          <mj-text align="left">This is estimated to continue until Friday 1 November at 06:00 PM </mj-text>
          <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="#979797" />
          <mj-text align="left" font-weight="700" padding-bottom="0px">What happend? </mj-text>
          <mj-text align="left" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px">
            <p>
              Part of Summer Lane outbound from Birmingham City Centre is currently closed due to emergency repairs to
              fix a broken gas main.
            </p>
            <p>NXWM 7 and Claribels 424 are currently diverted and not serving 2 stops on Summer Lane.</p>
            <p>The stops at Hampton Street and Lower Loveday Street are closed and services are not stopping here.</p>
            <p>The diversion route is via Constitution Hill, Henritta Street, Summer Lane then normal line of route.</p>
            <p>
              Services inbound towards Birmingham City Centre are unaffected and will continue to use normal line of
              route.
            </p>
